            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school communication system is very poor. The management and Principal are least interested in parents' feedback, complaints and any damage control. It also shows how much they value your child. The coordinator inculcate a sense of fear among the kindergarten kids. She is still following 70's education system where she can yell and shout on any parent, or kid . I strongly feel the principal sense of secularism is twisted. If by mistake you will say in her room that your kid enjoyed attending puja or activities in earlier schools then she will shut you up saying \"OUR SCHOOL IS SECULAR\" . \nThough you do see girls in scarfs in the school premises. \nWe are not sure if its a good ground for over all development of the child . \nSchool chose not to reply to any of your comains or emails and are most indifferent. ",
