            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Billabong High International School, Noida, is an incredible institution that truly prioritizes the holistic development of its students.\nThe school boasts state-of-the-art facilities, a diverse range of extracurricular activities, and a well-rounded curriculum that fosters both academic and personal growth. The faculty is not only highly qualified but also dedicated and approachable, ensuring that each child receives individual attention and guidance.\nThe administration is organized and responsive, making communication easy and effective.\nThe environment here encourages creativity, innovation, and critical thinking, preparing students for the challenges of the future.\nI highly recommend this school to any parent looking for a nurturing and enriching learning experience for their child.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
