          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the finest schools I have been to. I left in 4th grade but I still remember how amazing those years were at Billabong and kangaroo kids. Can't get the picture out of my mind. I wish to be a child again and study here. I would say don't think just get your child admitted here, it will be a lifetime experience for them.",
